<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Erkinger von Seinsheim</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Gefangennahme von fünf Räubern, die drei Bürger zu Nürnberg bei der Rückreise von Frankfurt am Main in einem Wald bei Ochsenfurt überfallen haben.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_441" id="220r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_441_r1l1"><expan>Erckıng<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>Saunſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> <expan>Hofmeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_441_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Erck </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_441_line_1576422919347_3616"><expan>hofmeiſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> /. 
<del rend="strikethrough"><gap reason="illegible"/></del> vvir laſſen ew vviſſen / daʒ dreẏ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l4">franckfürt herheim geʒogen ſein wolten / vnd als ſie gen <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l5">komen / vnd auſʒ der Stat herauſʒ giengen / da <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> funff 
<add><ab facs="#facs_441_line_1576422936780_3626">die </ab></add> auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l7">auſʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat giengen 
<del rend="strikethrough"> cʒu Jn </del> / vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">wolt </del> geſellten ſich cʒu Jn 
<add><ab facs="#facs_441_r1l6">vnd <expan>ſprache<ex>n</ex></expan> / ſie <expan>beſorgte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſich </ab></add> vnd gıengen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l9">mit Jn vncʒ gen Ochſſenfürt vnd da <expan>belıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſie beẏ <expan>eınand<ex>er</ex></expan> v̈ber nacht 
<add><ab facs="#facs_441_r1l8">beẏ <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> wirt </ab></add> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l10">des morgens da komen ſie <expan>miteinand<ex>er</ex></expan> in ein holcʒ da wurffen die fünff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l12"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> darnẏder vnd <expan>name<ex>n</ex></expan> Jn vvas ſie heten / Nu kent ſie <expan>de<ex>r</ex>ſ<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_441_line_1576422959021_3641"><expan>gege<ex>n</ex>w<ex>er</ex>tıg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> vvol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l13">cʒeiger dıcʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd maint ſie cʒeſuchen / ancʒegreiffen vnd cʒu gevencknüſʒ </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l14">
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒebringen </del> / <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> Ob derſelb 
<del rend="strikethrough"> o </del> Jr <expan>eıne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mer <expan>ẏend<ex>er</ex>t</expan> anköm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> betret </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l16">
<add><ab facs="#facs_441_line_1576423138803_3766">vnd ew dar </ab><ab facs="#facs_441_line_1576423144550_3771">ynne <expan>anruffe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_441_line_1576423148912_3776">vvürde </ab></add> daʒ Jr Jm <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvillen ewr hilff vnd <expan>furdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darcʒu 
<del rend="strikethrough">wenden </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_441_line_1576422983112_3653">beweiſen vnd </ab></add> tun </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l18">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd auch ewn förſch cʒu Ochſſenfürt beẏ dem vvirt darnach <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> wollet / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l20">daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">dieſelb </del> ſie cʒu vencknüſʒ kömen / So vvolten 
<del rend="strikethrough"> wir </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_441_line_1590588964344_43">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſie </del></ab></add>
<add><l>die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </l></add> nach Jn <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_441_r1l22">recht iſt / vnd tut <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> als etc das <expan>vvoll<ex>en</ex></expan> etc</ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_441" id="220r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Ercking<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>Saunsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan></add>, wir lassen ew wissen, daz
                        drey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> von Franckfürt herheim gezogen sein wolten,
                        und als sie gen <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> komen und ausz der stat
                        herausz giengen, da <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> funff, <add>die</add> auch
                        ausz <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> stat giengen, und gesellten sich czu in
                            <add>und <expan>sprache<ex>n</ex></expan>, sie
                                <expan>besorgte<ex>n</ex></expan> sich</add>, und giengen mit in
                        uncz gen Ochssenfürt und da <expan>belib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sie
                                bey<expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan> über nacht <add>bey
                                    <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> wirt</add>; und des morgens da komen
                        sie <expan>miteinand<ex>er</ex></expan> in ein holcz, da wurffen die fünff
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> darnyder und <expan>name<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        in, was sie heten; nu kent sie <expan>de<ex>r</ex>s<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<add><expan>gege<ex>n</ex>w<ex>er</ex>tig<ex>er</ex></expan></add> wol
                        czeiger dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, ob derselb ir <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mer <expan>yend<ex>er</ex>t</expan> anköm
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> betret <add>und ew dar ynne
                                    <expan>anruffe<ex>n</ex></expan> würde,</add> daz ir im
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        willen ewr hilff und <expan>furdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darczu <add>beweisen
                            und</add> tun wollet, daz sie czu vencknüsz kömen. So wolten die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>  nach in
                            <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> als recht ist. Und tut
                                <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan> als etc. Das
                            <expan>woll<ex>en</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
